{"tid":1425624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要！！請推！！］有失明手足呼籲唔好搞交通燈","createTime":"2019-08-06T19:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:20:08.000Z","uid":260764,"like":95,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"c67218d5d9148044072b322739222cef92ac9461","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"Bread Bao :<br />\n懇請分享出去，希望唔好破壞交通燈😟，交通燈聲音對於我哋睇唔到嘅朋友係相當相當之緊要，一般人判斷覺得安全情況下見到冇車照過馬路<br />\n或者兜路 搵天橋代替😉<br />\n但係我哋睇唔到嘅朋友，通常只會揀一條自己最熟悉嘅路去行，交通燈失靈冇聲音，我哋就唔敢過馬路啦，未必知道附近有乜嘢路可以代替，交通燈聲音除咗協助我哋安全過馬路之外，最重要係可以幫我地定位大約知道自己身處喺邊一度🥺眼睛唔方便真係有苦自己知😢大家繼續加油，我睇唔到，心仍然同大家一齊嘅，比胡椒噴霧噴到眼睛一樣會痛一樣會流眼水，我同大家嘅血顏色係一樣嘅🙌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CN2KALa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCN2KALa.png&h=0a74f96f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGcR0bR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGcR0bR.png&h=5fbcb715&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5dd6b0debd22e6c141297cf789e4fe03c8aefd6","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:08:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9baea0c57081948ebd287e9efee685b1cbd4dc37","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:09:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76e91a501247ab96b3ab3873c9a8558ade7f0d73","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:09:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a508a9c571bfbc5b3ceac542d7e423d67a7852d","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:09:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26b55a0c9c8bdde4fc6144843cd7dec21437354d","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1ba41ec3e5899a9e638cc89e8f62f798d589f28","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:10:31.000Z","msg":