0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:04:36.000Z","msg":"先不論搞交通燈既意義同影響<br />\n<br />\n呢位失明人士面包曾經喺大埔谷強烈譴責示威者暴力，令活動變質，話好後悔之前參加過遊行，話義士騎劫晒個和平活動！然後因爲太多人屌9佢，佢馬上del post"},{"pid":"24bc8cfed246c4a192f83280c9cdf017be4b9a18","tid":1425624,"uid":25025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:55:37.000Z","msg":"我唔係盲，但交通燈咪有舊黃色好似mouse咁嘅嘢既？<br />\n嗰舊嘢摸下面有粒的，會跟住交通燈個聲嚟跳，會知道佢紅定綠, even冇聲。<br />\n<br />\n當然唔知破壞咗仲work唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7d0f03b9240305757305fbcee290d28bff2e44","tid":1425624,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21b2f36d76c187734a76f1b41f70b4333b4c42d","tid":1425624,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a188333c4ade233d681cc22c08bffb5dce525c2f","tid":1425624,"uid":259329,"like":12,"dislike":42,"score":-30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:15:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:05:42.000Z","msg":"[找亮點]到底係狗扮暴徒定有黑社會扮狗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc8e69f50ee64e3f0fc98829edac19e60996ba0","tid":1425624,"uid":185162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:33:11.000Z","msg":"一定要推"},{"pid":"404fa75e344177fc1d73a49913f04a18131f8274","tid":1425624,"uid":260764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:49:35.000Z","msg":"失明人士唔係單係麵包一個<br />\n點解要因為麵包之前講嘅嘢要妄顧同一類人嘅生命安全？<br />\n我睇唔通<br />\n<br />\n你放火燒狗屋度閘都唔會傷到人<br />\n但係失明人士通常一個人過馬路，真係俾車車親咁點算？<br />\n失明人士點算？<br />\n呢場抗爭點算？<br />\n你勇武到要攞人命嘅話點解唔係去攞啲奸官同啲狗嘅命？<br />\n<br />\n唔鐘意都要講，唔贊同無差別殺人"},{"pid":"2bac9956c8c55b6ee239a21d2adb0a78d5b0327c","tid":1425624,"uid":1